{"tid":1655072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（將軍澳人入）想知將軍澳會唔會搞個尋冤待雪既遊行？","createTime":"2019-10-15T01:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T05:48:15.000Z","uid":89229,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e2558f32c0e8ada2060d7fe9f8403e562b52d945","tid":1655072,"uid":89229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:39:02.000Z","msg":"游泳健將跳海自殺已經夠離奇 <br />\n而家重要有段片：1. 首先聽佢既語氣已經一啲都唔消極 2. 一個識得嬲 重要將佢既anger外化，指向番警察既人又點會自殺？ 重有個段剪得離奇既cctv片<br />\n<br />\n段片已經好清楚 陳彥霖係我地手足，當日200+1，我地可以出黎悼念梁烈士，今次我地點可以唔做野？<br />\n<br />\n目前至少我地至少可以做既野：<br />\n1. 繼續去vtc 向陳烈士悼念獻花，至少要有太子地鐵站既sound bite<br />\n2. 舉行一次將軍澳既地區遊行，至少要正正式式向vtc施壓，要佢地交番全段cctv片出黎，<br />\n3. 文宣，煲大番件事，等淺藍，中立撚都關注到件事<br />\n4. 大家一齊諗！"},{"pid":"8b05bf3bc44d1f5d0d20d896e51f5f229f86246f","tid":1655072,"uid":89229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:40:22.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"dfca6a3d036350408747bd4937cdc8ee332b9842","tid":1655072,"uid":89229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:43:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b848421bb99a8fcd0ad56aefdf3bf16576ea1ca6","tid":1655072,"uid":89229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:46:20.000Z","msg":"推到將軍澳人肯入黎！"},{"pid":"0efbdba56c5b2eb2f2f105f628870199b1a124d8","tid":1655072,"uid":89229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:49:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"115b0fdfbb568d0ad4b2f1943c2903f3157d3e0e","tid":1655072,"uid":89229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:53:14.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"d3bda58ed1b66f2ee1f49dce3b724406e83b65c9","tid":1655072,"uid":209897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:54:02.000Z","msg":"光復將軍澳"},{"pid":"9c0aa60e7835413dc3b70dfe6b21694df5fb8351","tid":1655072,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:54:20.000Z","msg":"調景嶺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我會日